<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ida7924e12-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s241"><num value="241">§ 241.</num><heading> Reference to chapters 1003, 1005, and 1007</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Provisions of law relating to the reserve components generally, including provisions relating to the organization and administration of the reserve components, are set forth in chapter 1003 (beginning with section 10101), chapter 1005 (beginning with section 10141), and chapter 1007 (beginning with section 10201) of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ida7924e13-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/103/337/dA/tXVI/s1661/a/2/B">Pub. L. 103–337, div. A, title XVI, § 1661(a)(2)(B)</ref>, <date date="1994-10-05">Oct. 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/2980">108 Stat. 2980</ref>, § 261; renumbered § 241, <ref href="/us/pl/114/328/dA/tXII/s1241/a/2">Pub. L. 114–328, div. A, title XII, § 1241(a)(2)</ref>, <date date="2016-12-23">Dec. 23, 2016</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/130/2497">130 Stat. 2497</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
